# Creating Application
1.  Domain layer        defined JPA entities and constraints -- using JPA & hibernate validator
2.  Repository layer    leverages spring data JPA -- using CrudRepository -- implement CRUD functionalities
3.  Controller layer    manages Web requests -- map http req to crud operations & passed data to view layer
4.  View Layer          (using thymeleaf templates)
                        user interaction


